examples.en: He is celebrated for his contributions to modern science.
He made many valuable contributions to the field of science.
The shrinkage in contributions is significant.
He has made inestimable contributions to our society.
Nothing could diminish the importance of his contributions.
Have you been making regular contributions to a pension plan?
As mayor, he made many positive contributions to the growth of the city.
Needless to say, any contributions of money will be gratefully received.
You can make annual contributions of up to $1000 in education savings accounts.
He self-deprecatingly downplays his own contributions to the festival's success.
The book is entertaining, but its contributions to Shakespearean scholarship are nugatory.
His office funneled millions of dollars in secret contributions to the re-election campaign.
Your contributions will go a long way towards helping children in need (=will help to reach a goal).
